name: DartsScorer
0:
”Alexa, open darts scorer”
”I scored one hundred and eighty”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: darts scorer
des:
Counts down the score from 501, or 301, for one to four players.

Notes:
Requires Follow-Up Mode to be On in Device Settings.
Say "Wait" before Alexa times out if you need more time to give your score.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
